{"tid":570353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上屆立法會大會，新民黨全面支持所有政府議案，其他建制派都唔弱","createTime":"2018-02-23T14:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T07:42:39.000Z","uid":16970,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c41d771dad74f3a1d757a40328f9d4529ff9fccf","tid":570353,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T14:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/28166973_2014216918818152_8774992510401002595_n.png?oh=3000ea3473a6984400ece2cf69674cb9&amp;oe=5B4950B2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F28166973_2014216918818152_8774992510401002595_n.png%3Foh%3D3000ea3473a6984400ece2cf69674cb9%26oe%3D5B4950B2&h=da914d25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底一個政黨要有幾愛政府，佢地先至會無論政府掟啲咩出嚟，都近乎十次有十次舉手贊成？<br />\n<br />\n形影相隨，愛情上可能係夠晒浪漫，但晌政治上就同個橡皮圖章冇分別了。<br />\n<br />\n註：２０１８年立法會補選，香港島選區參選人為區諾軒、伍廸希、任亮憲及新民黨陳家佩，九龍西選區參選人為姚松炎、民建聯鄭泳舜及蔡東洲，新界東選區參選人為黃成智、方國珊、陳玉娥、民建聯鄧家彪、趙佩玉及新民主同盟范國威。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fish.flavour/posts/2014216945484816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffish.flavour%2Fposts%2F2014216945484816&d=1AXYoDBdgTSqOkzXM491uywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=1304cfec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fish.flavour/posts/2014216945484816</a>"},{"pid":"1a21a70ebf84636baf4f468cec879d1f70dbf4dc","tid":570353,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T17:50:31.000Z","msg":"推下先."},{"pid":"7d08cb91e28789d81fa50947b63b93929360e0b6","tid":570353,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T17:58:30.000Z","msg":"因為人地有黨員係行政會議入面"},{"pid":"30c17259ca1487c5fb3c935594bb82727c098d16","tid":570353,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7d08cb91e28789d81fa50947b63b93929360e0b6","tid":570353,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T17:58:30.000Z","msg":"因為人